8. The display of claim 7 wherein said information insert is fabricated of a transparent material and comprises: 
a first pocket having upper and lower edges; 
a second pocket attached to said upper edge of said first pocket; and 
a third pocket attached to said lower edge of said first pocket; 
said second pocket having a lower edge, said third pocket having an upper edge, said lower edge of said second pocket spaced above said upper edge of said third pocket.

