a plurality of casket portions representing a plurality of casket choices from which the customer may select are displayed on said shelves; and 
a plurality of casket information modules are displayed on said lateral side portions of said back wall, each of said information modules corresponding to one of said plurality of casket portions and including an upstanding lip on a back edge thereof, said lip being received in one of said horizontal grooves thereby cantilevering said information module from said back wall.

