60. A viewing room for displaying a body of a deceased, said viewing room comprising: 
a vertical back room wall; 
a pair of vertical side room walls cooperating with said back room wall to form one end of said viewing room; 
a pair of vertical, horizontally spaced apart wing walls cooperating with said back room wall to form an alcove; 
a casket positioned within said alcove; and 
a body positioned in said casket.
